l?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MxpCEk.jpg&h=30078c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7f2MQZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7f2MQZm.jpg&h=2a3930a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXmaycH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXmaycH.jpg&h=3e781cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢整嘅唔係日清唔係出前一丁，係日本人原來最熟悉嘅拉麵味道，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">sapporo 一番(サッポロ一番)</span></strong>味噌拉麵。 劇中唔會避嫌唔提牌子，仲大大個close up喺包裝，佢同同事談論最愛sapporo一番乜味，壓倒性味噌味贏醬油味。 喺港劇絕對唔會大刺刺講明同埋影埋煮咩牌子嘅食物，如果有都係KFC式植入式廣告，但依套劇係漫改，sapporo一番亦唔係買咗廣告植入，尋晚播完後網上反應仲勁好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iG4O4jM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiG4O4jM.jpg&h=ff994d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wOsArs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wOsArs.jpg&h=69e8cccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3egBtMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3egBtMt.jpg&h=bb5ec78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpFZrx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpFZrx9.jpg&h=06e23a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCSXXEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCSXXEQ.jpg&h=8b97247e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtwhER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtwhER.jpg&h=3fd0fe12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQeZTf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQeZTf.png&h=57cbf3d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n札幌一番味噌原來出咗51年了，味道同埋包裝都好懷舊 ，但就一直係SANYO FOODS.嘅招牌商品。 雖然比安藤百福嘅日清雞麵遲出咗10年，但就係同出前一丁同一年推出，咁多年嚟，味噌味嘅拉麵佢係原祖兼領導，連啲廣告都成為經典。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBNQydm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBNQydm.jpg&h=08e70efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6FKCE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6FKCE1.jpg&h=af3323b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0FR16H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0FR16H.jpg&h=aa226d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiEfKj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiEfKj3.jpg&h=06e0862e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbTcrZYe7dA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIbTcrZYe7dA&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8dHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=6e727f28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbTcrZYe7dA</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返套劇，原來日本人認真咁煮即食麵時都好講究吓，真係好想跟住煮吓，網上亦有好多youtuber整 札幌一番味噌拉麵嘅教學片，大家有興趣可睇下。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p87V3jCCXWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp87V3jCCXWA&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8dHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=bb5111a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p87V3jCCXWA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=サッポロ一番みそラーメン\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fresults%3Fsearch_query%3D%E3%82%B5%E3%83%83%E3%83%9D%E3%83%AD%E4%B8%80%E7%95%AA%E3%81%BF%E3%81%9D%E3%83%A9%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A1%E3%83%B3&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8dHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=09ea4a0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=サッポロ一番みそラーメン</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T23:38:17.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠都算絕世好男人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1137639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1137639</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度呀原由柏実，屎忽鬼，返入黎啦，睇下你幾撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵埋篇報導比你呀，喂，邊度吊頸呀？話我知我點死撐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪搶完口柒左扮睇唔到先得咖，唔好以為頂撚原咀柒左咁易走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪潛水啦，屌你老母屎忽鬼，縮左入你老豆屎眼呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}